20/04/2003
PRISTINA, Kosovo, Serbia-Montenegro -- German Defence Minister Peter Struck cheered his country's troops in Kosovo on Friday (18 April) when he jumped on stage wearing a Blues Brothers-like black hat and dark glasses. His rendition of Jailhouse Rock won wild applause from the crowd. The 60-year-old minister's interpretation of <I>Mathilde</I> was also followed by cheers and calls for an encore. Stuck said he was pleased to spend Easter with the troops in Prizren. (AFP - 18/04/03)
